<div style="background:#FFC569;"><b>Persons</b></div>
<p><i>Ancient</i><br /></p>
<p><a href="/wiki/Gautama_Maharishi" title="Gautama Maharishi">Gautama</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Jaimini" title="Jaimini">Jaimini</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Kanada" title="Kanada">Kanada</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Maharshi_Kapila" title="Maharshi Kapila">Kapila</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Markandeya" title="Markandeya">Markandeya</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Pata%C3%B1jali" title="Patañjali">Patañjali</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Valmiki" title="Valmiki">Valmiki</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Vyasa" title="Vyasa">Vyasa</a><br /></p>
<p><i>Medieval</i><br />
