<li>The Teachings of Ramana Maharshi in his own words, by Arthur Osborne (<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/8188018155" class="internal">ISBN 81-88018-15-5</a>) PDF<sup id="cite_ref-60" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-60" title=""><span>[</span>61<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
<li>Day by Day with Bhagavan by A Devaraja Mudaliar (<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/8188018821" class="internal">ISBN 81-88018-82-1</a>). An account of daily discussions during the period 1945 to 1947.</li>
<li>Gems from Bhagavan, by A. Devaraja Mudaliar</li>
<li>Maha Yoga, by 'Who' (Lakshmana Sharma), Rev 2002 (<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/8188018201" class="internal">ISBN 81-88018-20-1</a>), PDF<sup id="cite_ref-61" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-61" title=""><span>[</span>62<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
