iam Rhys Davids">T.W.&#160;Rhys Davids</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Seongcheol" title="Seongcheol">Seongcheol</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sogyal_Rinpoche" title="Sogyal Rinpoche">Sogyal Rinpoche</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Robert_Thurman" title="Robert Thurman">Robert Thurman</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Richard_Gombrich" title="Richard Gombrich">Richard Gombrich</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Chah_Subhatto" title="Chah Subhatto">Chah Subhatto</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Nanavira_Thera" title="Nanavira Thera">Nanavira Thera</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Thanissaro_Bhikkhu" title="Thanissaro Bhikkhu">Thanissaro Bhikkhu</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Bhikkhu_Bodhi" title="Bhikkhu Bodhi">Bhikkhu Bodhi</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Nyanaponika_Thera" title="Nyanaponika Thera">Nyanaponika Thera</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Jack_Kornfield" title="Jack Kornfield">Jack Kornfield</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Gil_Fronsdal" title="Gil Fronsdal">Gil Fronsdal</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Seung_Sahn" title="Seung Sahn">Seung Sahn</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Kitaro_Nishida" title="Kitaro Nishida">Kitaro Nishida</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Dzongsar_Jamyang_Khyentse_Rinpoche" title="Dzongsar Jamyang Khyentse Rinpoche">Khyentse Norbu</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Daisetz_Teitaro_Suzuki" title="Daisetz Teitaro Suzuki" class="mw-redirect">D